metadata.name: Good Morning (GM) Fam
metadata.description:
GM everyone.

Saying Good Morning, just starts the day off in a good way. Whenever I see people say it, I get a warm feeling inside, like I'm in a space where people actually care!

When we say GM, we MEAN GM! Even if you aren't having the greatest start to the day, we still say it because we want the best for others. I was never one to see it with friends (and even family), but the NFT and Photography space is a different community. And that's just it, community! Where we say GM to not just say good morning, but to let others know we are here and we are ready to take on the day!

I hope this piece lets know you that no matter what, I want you to have a good morning because you deserve to have one. It's a little piece of me because everyone has given me so much value and continues to add value to me in ways I cannot repay.

So this one is for you, GM FAM GM!
